query:
SELECT 
  poi.id,
  poi.pickingOrderId,
  poi.productId,
  poi.requestedQuantity,
  p.sku,
  p.description
FROM pickingOrderItems poi
JOIN products p ON p.id = poi.productId
WHERE poi.pickingOrderId IN (
  SELECT smi.pickingOrderId 
  FROM shipmentManifests sm
  JOIN shipmentManifestItems smi ON smi.manifestId = sm.id
  WHERE sm.manifestNumber = 'ROM-1769734935811'
);
